    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A. Anderson, a member of the\nwalters union, caught yesterday\nafternoon sticking an unfair\"\nposter on an advertisement in\nfront of II. A. Harbles' restaurant\non Riverside avenue, was ar\nraigned in police court this after\nnoon and his case was continued\ntill April 20 on his own recognize\nance.\n\n\nThe walters union did not stand\nbehind Anderson in his act, which\nwas in violation of an injunction,\naccording to Secretary Cardamone\nof that union."
    }
